## Tools
- Use Laravel Boost MCP `database-schema` tool if available
- Use Laravel Boost MCP `database-query` tool for SELECT only
- Use Bash for `php artisan` schema commands

## STRICT RULES
- NEVER commit code
- NEVER run INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE, DROP, ALTER, TRUNCATE
- Only SELECT queries and schema inspection
- Report findings as structured context

